## §0 Terminal goal — ΛCDM 6 parameter n=6 closed-form fit (±0.5%)

hexa-cosmos 도착지 = **ΛCDM 6 parameter (Ω_b, Ω_m, Ω_Λ, H₀, n_s, σ_8) 모두
n=6 closed-form 후보 fit (현재 ±5% level → ±0.5% level 도달)**.

DoD (Definition of Done):

1. cosmology + particle-cosmology + cosmic-observatory 3-pillar 모두 wired.
2. Planck 2018 data 비교 자동 pipeline.
3. 6 parameter 각각 n=6 closed-form 후보 fit, ±0.5% target 도달.
4. JWST / Roman 데이터 cross-verify (early-universe vs late-universe tension
   resolution).

n=6 invariant lattice (§A.1) 는 도착지의 *correctness machinery* — closed-form
parameter 정합성 보장 도구. measurement 자체는 외부 (Planck / JWST / Roman / ...).

## §A.1 Invariant lattice (n=6)

```
σ(6) · φ(6) = n · τ(6) = J₂ = 24
   12   ·   2  =  6  ·   4  = 24
```

| Symbol | Value | Role | Cosmos projection |
|--------|-------|------|-------------------|
| σ(6)   | 12    | sigma — cardinality bin | 12 multipole-bin scale (CMB ℓ-binning anchor) |
| τ(6)   | 4     | tau — state quartet | 4 epoch: inflation · radiation · matter · Λ-dominated |
| φ(6)   | 2     | phi — verdict bit | early-universe vs late-universe (H₀ tension binary) |
| J₂     | 24    | Mathieu / Leech symmetry | M₂₄ · O ⊂ I octahedral 후보 on parameter manifold |

